bookTitle: Oz: The Wonderful Wizard of Oz
bookAuthors: Eric Shanower, Skottie Young, L. Frank Baum
Plot: When Kansas farm girl Dorothy flies away to the magical Land of Oz, she fatally flattens a wicked witch, liberates a living scarecrow and is hailed by the Munchkin people as a great sorceress but all she really wants to know is: how does she get home?
